{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732480/extras/new_eh_steam_library_logo.png?t=1732758679\" />The Fortress of Emery is one of the last bastions where humanity has been able to remain safe, thanks to the energy provided by the Emery crystals. After hundreds of years of peace, all its inhabitants live calmly without too many worries, but sometimes the smallest everyday action can lead to the greatest of catastrophes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this action JRPG inspired by SNES classics, you'll step into the shoes of Lug, an apparently ordinary boy who will fight against all odds to defend his village and uncover unsettling secrets long buried in oblivion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732480/extras/Attack_GIF.gif?t=1732758679\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Enjoy an exciting story with different endings based on your choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover various types of weapons that you can upgrade and evolve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Engage in real-time combat where you can use special attacks and magic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Confront formidable bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Solve puzzles to progress through dungeons, as not everything is brute force.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732480/extras/Magic.gif?t=1732758679\" />\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732480/extras/EH_puzzle2_GIF.gif?t=1732758679\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>A world full of secrets awaits you. Get ready to face all kinds